simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Implements the Noop command that demonstrates the TO task is alive

simplesect.title: Command Verification
simplesect.para:
Successful execution of this command may be verified with the following telemetry:
TO_CMDACPTCNT - command counter will increment
The TO_CMD_INF_EID informational event message will be generated when the command is received

simplesect.title: Error Conditions
simplesect.para:
This command may fail for the following reason(s):
Command packet length not as expected

simplesect.title: Evidence of failure may be found in the following telemetry:

listitem.para: TO_CMDRJCTCNT - command error counter will increment

simplesect.title: Criticality
simplesect.para: None

simplesect.title: Description
simplesect.para: Resets the to housekeeping counters

simplesect.title: Command Verification
simplesect.para:
Successful execution of this command may be verified with the following telemetry:
TO_CMDACTPCNT - command counter will be cleared
TO_CMDRJCTCNT - command error counter will be cleared
The TO_CMD_INF_EID debug event message will be generated when the command is executed
